{"title":"Spend and outcome tool (SPOT)","public_updated_at":"2017-02-16T00:00:00Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Public health teams and commissioners can:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>download a bespoke factsheet for your local authority or <abbr title=\"clinical commissioning group\">CCG</abbr> from the UK Government Web Archive</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>compare against other local authorities or <abbr title=\"clinical commissioning groups\">CCGs</abbr></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>look at spend against a selection of outcomes across public health interventions and frameworks, including the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.phoutcomes.info\">Public Health Outcomes Framework</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>identify programmes with outcomes that are significantly different to similar local authorities or <abbr title=\"clinical commissioning groups\">CCGs</abbr>, that may need more analysis</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Watch the video below for guidance on how to use the tool.</p>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OIvjbqq0pDo\">How to use the spend and outcome tool</a></p>\n\n<p>If you have any questions or feedback, email <a href=\"mailto:healtheconomics@phe.gov.uk\">healtheconomics@phe.gov.uk</a>.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2017-02-16T00:00:00.000+00:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_2083975\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/611721/spend-and-outcome-tool-local-authorities.xlsm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/assets/pub-cover-a380604bb953dc22ac9dcfbf3cc65598327f493c37b09ac497c45148cbaa21b1.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a aria-describedby=\"attachment-2083975-accessibility-help\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/611721/